Name: Traffic Command: Reborn
About the game: Traffic Command Reborn - Take command of the traffic in the streets, redirecting cars, and telling them when it is okay to stop, and when it is okay to go. One big game of Red light green light keeps you on your feet in this addicting traffic driving game. The game contains: - nice music, - nice graphics Reworked the mechanics of machine behavior, and added new levels. The goal of the game is to score as many points as possible in a round, and avoid an accident on the road. Take on the challenge, adjust traffic lights, control the traffic situation!
